name: second-floor bardo 2/4
description:
Patiently, a pillar fulfills its role as the outer edge of a gentle square. The concrete creates a boundary, a shape that helps us see the trees. 
What lies beyond this familiar frame, which has become something of a home? The forest.


second-floor bardo is a 4-piece series/fixed set. The subject is a small pool on the second floor of a mine that has reached the end of its first lifecycle.
